\name{r_score}
\alias{r_score}
\title{r-score}
\usage{
r_score(x, x0)
}
\arguments{
\item{x}{A numeric matrix. The training set genotypic information matrix can be given as genotype matrix \(coded by -1, 0, 1\) or principle component matrix.}

\item{x0}{A numeric mareix. The test set genotypic information matrix can be given as genotype matrix \(coded by -1, 0, 1\) or principle component matrix.}
}
\description{
This function calculate r-score by given training set and test set.
}
